title: Did Raymundo Propose Over Birthday Weekend? + Bobby Had To Scold Woman During Comedy Show + Lunchbox Gets Letter From His Bank

description:
Bobby asked Raymundo about his birthday weekend and if he proposed to his longtime girlfriend. Bobby talks about having to scold a woman at his comedy show over the weekend. Lunchbox got a letter from his bank about the money that accidentally showed up in his account.
